<strong><font color="#e50000">OUR THREE LOCATIONS</font></strong><br><br>
<font color ="#C0C0C0">Click on an image to open VRChat's website.</font>
<br><br>
	<strong>VRCHAT KMART</strong> (MAIN STORE)
<br><br>
<a href="https://vrchat.com/i/booty-atriedesaustin-82e9b">
<img src="../images/mainstore1.png"></a>
<p>
A 1:1 scale recreation of the real store Ericirno worked at. This location features all the
accommodations you would find at a real Kmart in 1992. Take a look under <a href="../wndwshop/wndwshop-stm.html"> Window Shop </a>
to see the full list. (Our corporate offices are here, too!)
<p>
<p>
	<strong>KMART EXPRESS</strong>
<br><br>
<a href="https://vrchat.com/home/launch?worldId=wrld_aeb82cfe-6875-41f9-af32-1e735a67e051">
<img src="../images/express2.png"></a>
<p>
The <i> Oculus Quest compatible </i> Saving Place! At about 1/3 the scale of the Main Store. This
location features certain departments including Fashion Accessories, Electronics, and
the Kmart Café Express featuring Little Caesars Pizza Station.
<p>
<p>
	<strong>SUPER VRCHAT KMART CENTER</strong><br>(COMING SOON!)
<br><br>
<a href="https://vrchat.com/home/launch?worldId=wrld_dc7ab61c-93d0-4952-8728-94880fd7cc4e">
<img src="../images/superk1.png"></a>
<p>
Super VRChat Kmart Center is everything you love about VRChat Kmart, and more! All the
accommodations of the main store plus a full service deli, bakery, and seafood counter,
fresh produce, full grocery, and more!
<br><br><br><br>
<strong><font color="#e50000">VRCHAT KMART CORPORATION PROPERTIES</font></strong><br>
<p>
	<strong>ALTERNATE TIMELINE</strong>
<br><br>
<a href="https://vrchat.com/home/launch?worldId=wrld_1269db04-a6e6-4de1-9c5b-66b0be4b30f1">
<img src="../images/alternate1.png"></a>
<p>
This location is permanently closed and undergoing investigation. Further details
will not be disclosed as of now. Contact VRChat Kmart's Security Team in case of
emergencies.

